### 1.1 Functional Requirements
- Provide conversational access to institutional data (R1)
- Integrate with LMS, Registration, Calendar, Email systems (R3)
- Notify students of deadlines and changes (RS2)
- Allow lecturers to post announcements (RL2)
- Provide dashboards and analytics (RS3, RL3)
- Support AI-based natural language processing (R5)
- Support SSO authentication (RS7)

### 1.2 Quality Attributes
- **Performance:** Responses under 2 seconds
- **Availability:** 99.5% monthly uptime
- **Security:** SSO + role-based access + privacy compliance
- **Scalability:** Handle 5,000+ concurrent users
- **Modifiability:** Support swapping or updating AI models
- **Usability:** Simple conversational interface (text + voice)

### 1.3 Constraints
- Must use cloud-native deployment
- Must comply with university data policies
- Must integrate with existing systems (LMS, Registration, Calendar)
- Must use AI/NLP models

### 1.4 Architectural Concerns
- Securing sensitive student and faculty data
- Ensuring data consistency across external systems
- Minimizing latency when AI model is used
- Reliable notifications and event scheduling
- Managing AI model updates without downtime
